type 'gulp' in terminal

AngularJS features:
- Directives
- MVC
- Data Binding (2-way)
- Expressions

AngularJS vs Angular
- Different paradigm
- MVC vs components
- More stable
- Less tooling

Binding
- Declare your ng-app
- AngularJS directives
- ng-model directive
- {{}} expression

Working with modules
- module(), ng-app
- controller(), ng-controller
- $scope

Booleans and Loops
- ng-show, ng-hide
- ng-if
- ng-repeat

AngularJS Services
- $http
- Runs with a server

Basic Filters
- currency
- number
- date
- lowercase, uppercase
- Use | and : characters

Array Filters
- limitTo:qty:start
- filter:keyword
- orderBy:key:reverse

Deep Linking
- ngRoute
- $routeProvider
- ng-view
- Defining controllers
